    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/fd7bf20aabe98738dacb24e703b807c1.poster.avif?t=1767729212\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/fd7bf20aabe98738dacb24e703b807c1.webm?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/fd7bf20aabe98738dacb24e703b807c1.mp4?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Best friends Sammy and Hannah are relaxing after a long day by playing their favorite tabletop role-playing game, <i>Beast Dungeon</i>. When Hannah distractedly pulls out their handheld and starts to play <i>DIGIBUBBLE BEAT DX</i>, gamemaster Sammy devises a crazy and twisted little fusion: <strong>BubbleBeast DigiDungeon</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/a048bd41537655ec7290e5c524406ca8.poster.avif?t=1767729212\" width=800 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/a048bd41537655ec7290e5c524406ca8.webm?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/a048bd41537655ec7290e5c524406ca8.mp4?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get into the flow with unique puzzle-rhythm mechanics across 5 vibrant levels! Match colored bubbles to the beat, defuse the Beasts’ attacks, and don't let that combo meter break!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/454ba645e081b9acd6728e2e76619649.poster.avif?t=1767729212\" width=800 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/454ba645e081b9acd6728e2e76619649.webm?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071280/extras/454ba645e081b9acd6728e2e76619649.mp4?t=1767729212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BubbleBeast DigiDungeon is a love letter to handheld console and mobile games of the early 2000s. Lose yourself in the vivid, hand-crafted cast of characters and the bouncy soundtrack inspired by breakbeat, classic RPGs, and 2000s pop. ✧':*✧':*</p>",
